                        <condition>
                           <ab type="conservation">This dark brown papyrus has many parts are covered by a layer of mud, especially at the right side. It has the left and bottom margins. Badly mutilated at the top and right sides. Some fibers are misaligned and frayed. It seems from some damages that the papyrus was vertically folded couple times. There are some lacunae at the middle.</ab>
                        </condition>
