                     </layoutDesc>
                  </objectDesc>
                  <handDesc>
                     <p>Written along the fibers in two hands; the body of the text is written in large upright and uncial cursive letters. The hand is practiced, neat and flourished. No diacritical signs are attested; second hand that wrote the last two lines is small-sized cursive and ligatured. Verso has one line written along the fibers.</p>
